<P>
HEALTH REFORM KILLED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Political cartoonist Paul Conrad's image in today's Times (Commentary, Sept. 
27) begs for clarification.Conrad, it wasn't Sen. Bob Dole who killed the 
Clinton health plan. It was the Clinton health plan that killed the Clinton 
health plan. And it happened all over America, not Amerika. 
</P>
<P>
 CAROLINE CLARK 
</P>
<P>
 Laguna Niguel 
</P>
