"trashed" health-care reform for their own agenda, I hope their constituency 
"trashes" them in upcoming elections. 
</P>
<P>
 Profit for pain sucks! A single-payer system is looking better all the time. 
</P>
<P>
 DERVA J. SNIDER 
</P>
