of this year compared to the preceding three months: 04,05,12,09,14 CURRENT 
LAST QUARTER 1. KPWR-FM 5.4 6.1 KLAX-FM 5.4 5.1 3. KFI-AM 4.7 3.8 4. KROQ-FM 
