but was designed with input from Hyundai Motor America's studio at its Fountain 
Valley headquarters. 
</P>
<P>
 Although the U.S. importer is based in Orange County, it is using Oregon for 
Accent's introduction because the countryside there is so photogenic. The 
company is hoping that the introduction will generate extensive newspaper and 
TV coverage. 
