<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA100594-0264 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 085812 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 5, 1994, Wednesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 5; Column 4 
